@base_url = http://localhost:7071/api

########## Edgewell Sales Genie hosted local Functions API ##########

### Health check
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Schick competitive positioning at Walmart
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?brand=schick&concerns=competitive%20positioning&preference=walmart&limit=3

### Summer promotion ideas for Banana Boat
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?brand=banana%20boat&concerns=summer%20promotion&preference=walmart&limit=3

### Back-to-school bundle ideas
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?concerns=back-to-school&preference=bundle&limit=3

### No-results fallback example
GET {{base_url}}/products/recommendations?brand=unknown-brand&finish=matte&maxPrice=10
